r" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="百万索赔凸显以色列多年战争的代价"&gt;增加了该基金可能出现短缺的风险&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;开源软件维护者&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;像 Anthropic 的 Mythos 这样的人工智能工具发现软件漏洞的速度比修复软件漏洞的速度要快，而小型开源团队正感受到压力。错误报告的激增正在使维护人员成为&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/3_k5ClxZDSZF7sbgZkuHMXmwIIoj6hVN6m9Rp1rYTg_Ssylv7vjqqHEaNlEu3zQ0Jwic7kequEQGOjR01b4k73w4lK1oeSVfFXlQJ9vyJR_WwE848GFMZNITEkLpTkVbXi-YmFJsUjCMxjUkG-42DbiDjNDrlgYYChGcHZml6uQYyHE9QDhQihIGoIlMI1FOFue3YdZ91ice7-22_Ab4pYwzGZkNoJtUc7YipVTBM9kFY7dM3KgFpxPQ4s0hnLvxexkfr_N8oZOlTV63QYwQxE8-HQayI9d_CucpRzPF2pf4NdNTUjbATFP2Dur5J_H7yW3nBMF7QUyXVsjNsImgAxOTyGye4rj8y4YhkgKTB-Zmwj_Ky_TSt2TxA-K2qhZJlZBQl-01v359oaKwfWHSo0w02pWZPJ5fuCRGewjDi8Eont4Sj2-m0rAGQ8E1TC2jz7sr32FKtPErtBtO1HfZw-R9DBJCojcvYwr2Bcmwo6pcC-QYmW3hXzdQL2Z354T4dBMOYYq1Srcuz1MQVwB3kQUA_8s07hHZ2Q/onvQi-qXvrFwFmfK5EcAQefCZRUvaIjd/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="人工智能发现的错误比开源团队能够应对的还要多"&gt;测试支撑互联网的系统的&lt;/a&gt;瓶颈。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;孟买居民&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;随着全球资本推动房地产繁荣，低收入居民被吸引参与重建交易，这将决定他们是否能够留下来。新公寓的承诺伴随着不确定性，从&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/2pA9BKz-ahAH1z8lpAWWzbn7xsj9lz3_QtPBA_Z708AlOwTucOPqtB1M7RndIYlEsE982ITrMP9BgVJ7WObzommHUB5NBkoD2_VLU8Y37HcaabxA9mD7aQerr_vupcybVnJk1pCduO-DNUvT1JmTE3hj9XChvc-vXxtCr8Pb46ke4qsksEOOL5fN8BSdB8QIW381CIfr1rjT4__Q_f_0MGxl_M3QED_9KrezKQmCJ_MDn8S_cAYiQT7vU0k357H0-lM7UIBgVdMSvJugWPGQtiUbwcqjVN2efVloHxsmIEm31Dx7nCZmdaX_hlERY3WuR0AbjArDQixqk5CE8-l7wq3UfUKjoyp95nbR-BO1Gxj8a2uEqWdUzSw3qYPyvGn3BpRuQe5QbVaJeS2LggPAOR6BbDF3lrBUwT3CkKM5XCwbikzsmwGdbQpbfNUOA5EExYzwWdtq-vTXPTDfgaEkPcLQ-VpzRxXm3HroBP19g2nIJg6YbZSsATYBjZ8lqimjp10kOu5FqGVqv7zQ0KTHdrpd/sTh-2hlKCHxzV7klYGqZrKTtTQc73GgE/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target=